      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has started to soften, add your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and <strong>tomato paste</strong> to the pan and cook for 2 min further or until fragrant</p><p>Tip: Add a drizzle of oil if the pan looks a little dry</p>",
