    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 350ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[525ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[700ml] </span><strong>cold</strong> <strong>water</strong> to the pan and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, add the<strong> halved green beans</strong> and your <strong>sultanas</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix, then<strong> </strong>reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for an initial 8 min</p>",
