      "instruction": "<p>After an initial 8 min, add the <strong>crispy</strong> <strong>meat-free chick'n </strong>and cook, covered, for 2 min further or until the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Tip: Add a little water if the rice is not cooked or the mixture is a little dry</p>",
